1. Drag and drop the SpawnAProjectile Script to Any of the Environment GameObject.
2. Now in the inspector Assign Player GameObject that has a Move Player Script Attached to it.
3. Also assign the point from where you are going to fire, keep this point a little ahead from the player to avoid collisions among colliders.
4. Now from the assets Select a projectile from Either Projectiles1 or Projectiles2 Folder and Assign it to the VFx list in the Inspector.
5. Enter Play mode to Test.


